```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant R as Researcher
    participant arX as arXiv
    participant GH as GitHub repo
    participant PWC as paperswithcode.com
    participant C as Community
    participant L as Leaderboard

    R->>arX: Upload paper (v1)
    R->>GH: Release code + weights
    R->>PWC: Submit benchmark entry
    PWC->>L: Add to ranking
    C->>GH: Attempt reproduction
    alt Reproduction succeeds
        C->>PWC: Confirm + reference
        L->>L: Entry stays climbs ranking
    else Reproduction fails
        C->>PWC: Flag concerns
        L->>L: Annotate / remove entry
        R->>arX: Upload revision (v2/v3)
    end
    Note over L: SoTA = top-ranked validated entry
    Note over L: Benchmark eventually saturates
    L->>PWC: New harder benchmark added
```
